2004-07-16  Martin Holters  <martin.holters@gmx.de>

	* board/go.c (go_score_game): Don't use utils_format_double(),
	format as user's locale specifies.
	* gui-gtk/gtk-goban-window.c (update_game_specific_information):
	Likewise.

